Description: AI-powered miniature repainting assistant
 AI Miniature Repainting is a machine learning-powered desktop application
 that provides real-time analysis, color suggestions, and technique guidance
 for detailed miniature painting. It leverages NVIDIA CUDA for GPU-accelerated
 processing when available, with automatic CPU fallback.
 .
 Features:
 - Real-time AI analysis of painting techniques
 - Intelligent color matching and suggestions
 - GPU acceleration support (NVIDIA CUDA)
 - Cross-platform compatibility (Windows, macOS, Linux)
 - Professional-grade image processing
